The license-default in this repo is provisional. The next Claude Code session
working with the curator is expected to confirm or change the license per the
open question recorded in HANDOFF_TO_NEXT_CLAUDE_CODE.json. Provisional
defaults are CC-BY-SA 4.0 for the methodology and documentation. Model-output
texts produced by the AI tools named in the field logs are reproduced here
under fair-use research-and-criticism premises pending a clearer multi-tool
licensing analysis; the curator and the next Claude Code session will sharpen
the licensing on those texts in subsequent commits.

This LICENSE file will be updated when the open question is resolved.
